      • getAuthCode

        public java.lang.String getAuthCode(int unit,
                           int port)
        fro a given Q330 unit at the site and the data port (dataport 0=admin port) return the current authorization code for the unit. If the admin port is authcode zero, then all data ports will also return zero.
        Parameters:
        unit - Q330 unit number, normally 0 or 1 if two Q330s are at the site
        port - The port number 0=admin port, 1=dataport 1, etc.
        Returns:
        A string with the hex auth code
